snippet.title: Fireside Hero trailer (early access)
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for Fireside Hero, a compact turn-based strategy with a twist. Hire adventurers, plan their movement, identify monster hideouts, and win tactical fights! 

Early access build version 0.9.3 
http://www.firesidehero.com
